The **Costa del Sol** continues to solidify its reputation as a premier destination for international corporate gatherings. Between May 20 and May 23, 2026, the prestigious **PROGOLD SUMMIT 2026** took place at the **Hotel Meliá Costa del Sol Centro de Convenciones** in Torremolinos, Málaga, Spain.

This high-profile corporate event brought together industry professionals for days of intensive networking, presentations, and strategic meetings. To ensure the ambitious presentation schedule met world-class standards, **Malaga Event Gear (MEG)** was brought on board to manage the technical production, delivering a seamless audiovisual environment for all attendees.

